For more information on how to download and run this demo you can go to the "&lt;span class="wikilink"&gt;&lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/view/Main.Documentation/Demos#HWarehousePacketDelivery283TierUse29"&gt;WarehousePacketDelivery(3 Tier Use)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;” at the "&lt;span class="wikilink"&gt;&lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/view/Main.Documentation/Demos"&gt;AITdev Demos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" page.
&lt;h4 class="heading-1-1-1"&gt;&lt;span id="HWarehousePacketDelivery28AITdevAspireRFID6TierUse2928See5BYouTubeVideo3Ehttp3A2F2Fwwwyoutubecom2Fwatch3Fv3D9f63eoFwEN45D29"&gt;Warehouse Packet Delivery (AITdev AspireRFID 6 Tier Use) (See &lt;span class="wikiexternallink"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f63eoFwEN4"&gt;&amp;#89;ouTube Video&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p class="paragraph"/&gt;&lt;center&gt;
