&lt;/center&gt;&lt;p class="paragraph"/&gt;&lt;strong class="strong"&gt;&lt;span class="wikiexternallink"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.ait.edu.gr/ait_web_site/Researcher/nkef/WarehouseEpcisPacketDeliveryDemo/WarehouseEpcisPacketDeliveryDemo.html"&gt;&amp;#83;ee the Demo's Video&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;p class="paragraph"/&gt;
